Package: MEAanalysis
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Analyse and Visualise Multi Electrode Array Single Electrode, Well, and Synchrony Data Downstream of AxIS Navigator 3.6.2 Software (Axion BioSystems) Processing
Authors@R: person(given = "Emily", 
                  family = "Gordon",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                  email = "emily.gordon@wadham.ox.ac.uk")
Maintainer: Emily Gordon <emily.gordon@wadham.ox.ac.uk>
Description: Functions to assist multielectrode array data analysis and exploration at the single electrode level utilising electrode burst list files produced
             by 'AxIS Navigator 3.6.2 Software' (Axion BioSystems). Compare bursting parameters between time intervals and recordings using the bar chart
             visualisation functions. Compatible with 12- and 24- well plates.
